stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> IDLE : Card Created

    %% ========== IDLE STATE ==========
    state IDLE {
        [*] --> idle_editable : is_editable = true
        [*] --> idle_locked : is_editable = false
        idle_editable : is_editable = true
        idle_locked : is_editable = false

        idle_editable --> idle_editable : User edits payload (on-update, sync, 3s)
        idle_editable --> idle_locked : Processor sets is_editable = false
        idle_locked --> idle_editable : Processor sets is_editable = true
    }

    %% ========== SYNC HOOKS (around IDLE) ==========
    note right of IDLE
        **Sync Hooks (Blocking, 3s timeout)**
        • on-update: Validates & transforms user edits
        • can-exit: Guards column exit permission

        **Retry Policy:**
        • 4xx → Fail fast (no retry)
        • 5xx/408/429 → Max 1 retry, exponential backoff
    end note

    %% ========== ASYNC TRANSITIONS ==========
    IDLE --> PROCESSING : Card enters Processing column (on-enter POST, 202 Accepted)

    IDLE --> PROCESSING : User clicks action button (on-action POST, 202 Accepted)

    %% ========== PROCESSING STATE ==========
    state PROCESSING {
        [*] --> processing_active : Spinner shown (UI locked)

        processing_active : processing_state = PROCESSING
        processing_active : is_editable = false (forced)

        processing_active --> processing_active : SLA timer running (max 24h)
    }

    note right of PROCESSING
        **Async Hook (ACK + Callback)**
        1. Orchestrator POSTs to Processor
        2. Processor returns 202 Accepted
        3. Processor does work (instant → 24h)
        4. Processor POSTs callback with token
        5. Orchestrator verifies & applies
    end note

    %% ========== CALLBACK OUTCOMES ==========
    PROCESSING --> IDLE : Callback Success (POST /callbacks/{token}, payload_updates applied)

    PROCESSING --> ERROR : SLA Breach (DLQ entry created, SLA expired)

    PROCESSING --> ERROR : Invalid Callback (security event logged)

    %% ========== ERROR STATE ==========
    state ERROR {
        [*] --> error_pending : Admin review required

        error_pending : processing_state = ERROR
        error_pending : is_editable = false (forced)
        error_pending : UI shows retry/override

        error_pending --> error_pending : Admin reviews DLQ
    }

    note right of ERROR
        **Dead Letter Queue (DLQ)**
        • Admin can RETRY (re-dispatch)
        • Admin can FORCE (override to IDLE)
        • Admin can CANCEL (move to error column)

        All admin actions logged as
        ACTION: ADMIN_OVERRIDE
    end note

    %% ========== ERROR RECOVERY ==========
    ERROR --> PROCESSING : Admin Retry

    ERROR --> PROCESSING : Admin Retry (Re-dispatch same context)

    ERROR --> IDLE : Admin Force Complete

    ERROR --> IDLE : Admin Force Complete (override to IDLE)

    %% ========== EXIT GUARD ==========
    IDLE --> IDLE : Move rejected (POST /can-exit, allowed = false)

    IDLE --> [*] : Card archived (can-exit = allowed, on-exit POST, fire-and-forget)

    %% ========== on-exit NOTE ==========
    note left of IDLE
        **on-exit (Fire-and-Forget)**
        Triggered AFTER successful exit.
        Orchestrator does NOT wait.

        ✅ Use for: cleanup, metrics, logs
        ❌ NEVER for: billing, compliance,
           mission-critical side effects
    end note

    %% ========== can-exit GUARD NOTE ==========
    note left of IDLE
        **can-exit (Sync Guard)**
        Called BEFORE every move.
        Default on timeout: allowed = false

        Archive Block Policy:
        Rejects if children are active
    end note
